
Open Gitbash >> 
type node-v  (to check the version of Nodejs)

Installation steps
npm init
////////////// webdriver io
npm install -save-dev webdriverio@4.13.2
//////////////mocha to structure our framework
npm install -save-dev mocha@5.2.0
/////////////selenium standalone for running the scripts, middleman between wdio and browser
npm install -save-dev selenium-standalone@6.15.3
/////////////run selenium standalone on machine
./node_modules/.bin/selenium_standalone install
//////////// settig the wdio file
./node_modules/.bin/wdio


/////////////running the test
node filename.js



////if the 4444 port if busy then, to know what is running on the port
netstat -ano |findstr:4444
////to kill the process  
taskkill / PID 8***(taks no) /F

